author: Home Repair Tutor
description: Toilet plumbing tip…I used a 1-1/2” x 9” steel plate to protect these water supply lines. Since I’m the one repairing the drywall and installing the baseboard, there’s no chance of me piercing the pipes. But it’s good to have the plate for future repairs 👍🏽#plumbing #homerenovation #homerepairtutor
